{"product_id":"be-the-damn-penguin-cinematic-antarctic-motivation-poster","title":"Be the Damn Penguin | Cinematic Antarctic Motivation Poster","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"127\" data-end=\"334\"\u003eA lone penguin walks away from the crowd—into the quiet, the cold, and the unknown. \u003cstrong data-start=\"211\" data-end=\"236\"\u003e“Be the damn PENGUIN”\u003c\/strong\u003e is a bold reminder to stop following the comfortable route and start choosing the meaningful one.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"336\" data-end=\"658\"\u003eThis design blends \u003cstrong data-start=\"355\" data-end=\"401\"\u003eminimal, ultra-cinematic Antarctic scenery\u003c\/strong\u003e with \u003cstrong data-start=\"407\" data-end=\"436\"\u003estrong typographic impact\u003c\/strong\u003e—massive negative space, soft misty mountains, and a subtle trail of footprints that pulls your eye forward. Perfect for anyone building discipline, chasing a bigger goal, or simply needing a daily nudge to stay different.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"660\" data-end=\"841\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"660\" data-end=\"676\"\u003ePerfect for:\u003c\/strong\u003e workspace walls, study setups, gyms, creative studios, dorm rooms, and gift ideas for friends who love motivation, minimal design, and documentary-style aesthetics.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"843\" data-end=\"857\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"843\" data-end=\"857\"\u003eHighlights\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul data-start=\"858\" data-end=\"1070\"\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"858\" data-end=\"933\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"860\" data-end=\"933\"\u003eClean, minimal composition with dramatic scale and calm blue-grey tones\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"934\" data-end=\"1006\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"936\" data-end=\"1006\"\u003eBold typography + subtle “meaning” copy for an editorial poster feel\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"1007\" data-end=\"1070\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1009\" data-end=\"1070\"\u003eHigh-impact wall presence without looking loud or cluttered\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1072\" data-end=\"1114\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"1072\" data-end=\"1081\"\u003eNote:\u003c\/strong\u003e Frame not included (print only).\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51367137640744,"sku":null,"price":119.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A5","offer_id":51367137673512,"sku":null,"price":79.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51367137706280,"sku":null,"price":149.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13x19\"","offer_id":51367137739048,"sku":null,"price":169.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/2_2e9f08eb-c9da-4f34-bc80-7fbc0d6f88de.webp?v=1769235043","url":"https:\/\/www.posterized.in\/products\/be-the-damn-penguin-cinematic-antarctic-motivation-poster","provider":"Posterized","version":"1.0","type":"link"}